Requisites
========================================

* Python 2.5+
* Django 1.2.x
* pycrypto
* B3 (http://www.bigbrotherbot.com)
Installation
========================================

Rename settings/60-local.pyconf.example to settings/60-local.pyconf
and edit with your database settings (KEEP the name 'default' on it)

Run python manage.py syncdb to setup database.
Run python manager.py addserver to add a server config (run manager.py help addserver for more info)
Run python manage.py runserver to start dev server and point browser to http://127.0.0.1:8000/